title: Inquisitor acervatus
text:
Inquisitor acervatus is a <a href="species">species</a> of <a href="sea%20snail">sea snail</a>, a marine <a href="gastropod">gastropod</a> <a href="mollusk">mollusk</a> in the <a href="family%20%28biology%29">family</a> <a href="Pseudomelatomidae">Pseudomelatomidae</a>, the turrids and allies.
Distribution.
This marine species occurs off <a href="Southern%20Australia">Southern Australia</a>.
